com.iutdijon.androiut2.util.zoom
Class DynamicZoomControl

java.lang.Object
  com.iutdijon.androiut2.util.zoom.DynamicZoomControl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Observer
public class DynamicZoomControl
extends Object
implements Observer

The DynamicZoomControl is responsible for controlling a ZoomState. It makes sure that pan movement follows the finger, that limits are satisfied and that we can zoom into specific positions. In order to implement these control mechanisms access to certain content and view state data is required which is made possible through the ZoomContentViewState.
